
0.7.0 2006-06-24 Andrew Wedgbury <wedge@sconemad.com>

	* New configurable pooled multi-threaded design.
	* Non-blocking outgoing connections.
	* Connection forwarding module.
	* Datagram support with virtual channels, making it very easy to write
	datagram servers.
	* TFTP (Trivial File Transfer Protocol) module.

0.6.0 2006-06-21 Andrew Wedgbury <wedge@sconemad.com>
	
	* Implement proper control structures in SconeScript.
	* Make HTTP module more compliant with HTTP/1.1.
	* Add HTTP profiles, can map different ports to different doc trees.
	* External program execution and streaming.
	* Execution of CGI programs from HTTP.
	* Protocol modules for IP, IP6, Bluetooth and Local.
	* Improve docs and add several example modules.
	* Add testbuilder module - an automated test build system with web 
	interface.

0.5.9 2005-11-15 Andrew Wedgbury <wedge@sconemad.com>
	
	* Test release.
	* Minor bugs and issues fixed following portability testing.

0.5.8 2005-11-09 Andrew Wedgbury <wedge@sconemad.com>
	
	* Test release.
	* Improved http module structure.
	* Better debug/assertion handling with logging.

0.5.7 2005-08-14 Andrew Wedgbury <wedge@sconemad.com>
	
	* Test release.
	* Cleaner sconed/sconex structure.
	* New protocol handlers for simple module.
	* Fix timezone support.

0.5.6 2005-07-05 Andrew Wedgbury <wedge@sconemad.com>
	
	* Test release.
	* Connection counter in stat module.
	* Command line options now conform to GNU standards.
	* HTTP dir/index module for producing directory listings, or
	  redirecting to index page, if exists.
	* Put together and expanded documentation, this is all in HTML format.
	* Tested and improved installer.

0.5.5 2005-06-05 Andrew Wedgbury <wedge@sconemad.com>

	* Test release.
	* Improve logging subsystem.
	* Improve SconeScript interpreter.

0.5.4 2005-04-07 Andrew Wedgbury <wedge@sconemad.com>

	* Test release.
	* Configurable module/log/conf paths for all modules.
	* Timezone support.
	* Win32 version runs as service.
	* Configurable mime module.
	* SSL improvements - multiple configurable channels.

0.5.3 2005-01-10 Andrew Wedgbury <wedge@sconemad.com>

	* Test release.
	* SconeScript interface to connection mapper.
	* Foreground config/test mode.

0.5.2 2004-12-27 Andrew Wedgbury <wedge@sconemad.com>

	* Test release.
	* Statistics module.
	* Simple TCP/IP services module.

0.5.1 2004-07-05 Andrew Wedgbury <wedge@sconemad.com>

	* Test release.
	* Added SconeScript configuration system.

0.5.0 2003-12-22 Andrew Wedgbury <wedge@sconemad.com>

	* Test release.
	* Project now in GNU style tree, using autoconf, automake and libtool,
	  which should allow better cross platform support.

